channel.description: Cutter Setup To activate passthrough, first set up the cutter to let objects pass through it. To do this, first open the lid, open the front compartment, and pull out the black tray. Image You will then see in the front and back 2 black screws. Image Twist these to remove them and the attached bar, and set them aside somewhere safe. Image You can then place the tray back in, and close the front and the lid.
